  ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE & MACHINE LEARNING
============================================================

Concept:     Mixture of Experts
Category:    Architecture
Definition:  Sparse model activating different expert subsets per token
Year:        2017
Researchers: Shazeer et al.
Applications:Large LLMs (Mixtral, rumored GPT-4)
Related:     Sparse activation, routing, scaling efficiency

Concept:     Constitutional AI
Category:    Alignment
Definition:  AI trained on principles via self-critique to reduce harm
Year:        2022
Researchers: Anthropic/Bai et al.
Applications:Claude safety and alignment
Related:     RLHF, harmlessness, helpfulness, honesty

Concept:     CNN
Category:    Architecture
Definition:  Convolutional filters detect spatial features hierarchically
Year:        1989
Researchers: LeCun et al.
Applications:Image classification, object detection
Related:     Pooling, feature maps, ResNet

============================================================
  DISEASES & MEDICINE
============================================================

Disease:     Influenza
Type:        Viral
Pathogen:    Influenza viruses
Transmission:Respiratory droplets
Symptoms:    Fever, chills, muscle aches
Treatment:   Oseltamivir, rest, fluids
Deaths/yr:   0.65M
Vaccine:     Yes (annual update)
Discovered:  1933

Disease:     Cardiovascular Disease
Type:        Metabolic
Pathogen:    Non-communicable
Transmission:Non-communicable
Symptoms:    Chest pain, shortness of breath
Treatment:   Statins, surgery, stents
Deaths/yr:   17.9M
Vaccine:     No (for most types)
Discovered:  Ancient

Disease:     HIV/AIDS
Type:        Viral
Pathogen:    HIV
Transmission:Sexual contact, blood
Symptoms:    Flu-like; then AIDS symptoms
Treatment:   Antiretroviral therapy (ART)
Deaths/yr:   0.65M
Vaccine:     No (in development)
Discovered:  1983

